  "translations": {
    "en": "And with the preceding chain of narration, Ali ibn Mahzyar reported from Ahmad ibn Muhammad, from Hammad ibn Uthman, who said: Ismail al-Jufi said: I heard Abu Jafar Muhammad ibn Ali, peace be upon them both, say:",
    "ur": "And with the preceding chain of narration, Ali ibn Mahzyar reported from Ahmad ibn Muhammad, from Hammad ibn Uthman, who said: Ismail al-Jufi said: I heard Abu Jafar Muhammad ibn Ali, peace be upon them both, say:",
